Newest Filings











Carlyle Private Equity Access Fund 2015, L.P.  Financing
Carlyle Private Equity Access Fund 2015, L.P. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  This is a new filing. Carlyle Private Equity Access Fund 2015, L.P. was able to sell $0. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 0 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2016-01-21. Carlyle Private Equity Access Fund 2015, L.P. is based in  1001 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE N.W. SUITE 220 SOUTH WASHINGTON 20004. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  N/A CARLYLE ACCESS GP 2015, L.L.C..





