Private Equity Software - Preqin Solutions, formerly Baxon Solutions









































































Go to Top













  
                        Call Us +44 (0) 203 207 0480						
                    





































Preqin Solutions










Solutions








We offer a fresh perspective for Private Equity firms wishing to complement their existing system infrastructure with a cloud solution that automate their portfolio company monitoring, performs their valuations, and streamlines their LP reporting. 
With the integration of Preqin performance data on over 8,500 private capital funds, in addition to LN, KS, PME+ and Direct Alpha PME methodologies, the system also gives you the ability to benchmark your performance against private or public markets on the fly.
 


 

MONITORING
Automate your Portfolio Company monitoring and reporting process – users access the cloud platform from anywhere at any time, access dynamic dashboards from all types of devices, create PDF’s, print reports and even integrate with Excel. + Request a demo
 

VALUATION
Shorten the valuation cycle and ensure consistency, transparency and traceability of each valuation exercise. The system can be customized to your needs, or you can choose from one of the existing templates. The enormous flexibility in the platform allows full compatibility with complex waterfalls, cap tables and different asset classes and valuation methodologies. + Request a demo

FUND ANALYSIS
Intuitive tool for dynamic analysis of portfolio and fund track records, including ‘slice and dice’ of IRRs, sensitivity analysis to future returns, ‘what if’ scenarios, exit planning and allows benchmarking against peer Private Equity funds with Preqin data. + Request a demo

LP REPORTING
The system enables Investor Relations teams to automate the entire LP reporting process. Powered through the Preqin Solutions Monitoring, Valuation and Fund Analyzer Modules; the data for every report comes from a consistent source. This tool has been designed for General Partners to save time as well as improving accuracy and proficiency in the reporting process.

All dashboards, reports and charts can be accessed from any device and are completely integrated with Microsoft Excel. The Preqin Solutions platform is designed to manage portfolios across different asset classes and investment strategies: traditional Buyouts, Venture Capital, Infrastructure, Real Estate, Debt and Fund of Funds.
Third party integration: With its state of the art API, the Preqin platform can integrate with any General Ledger or CRM system allowing consistent information across your back and front office systems, avoiding manual re-entry of data.
 








 







                    
                                        
