Helping you achieve your organization's mission
Northern Trust understands the challenges that nonprofits face in today’s uncertain economic environment, and are committed to supporting you in effectively and efficiently achieving your mission.
Working with endowments and foundations worldwide, Northern Trust provides a wide spectrum of sophisticated investment solutions, strategic insights and world-class resources. We can help you develop your mission, create the strategy to achieve it and provide broad-based administrative and investment oversight of your program.
Our Services
Investment Management for Non-Profits
Northern Trust's fiduciary responsibilities guide our investment management decisions. We seek to add value through an investment process that is driven by your organization's goals and includes a wide spectrum of investment capabilities that can be tailored to your needs.
World-Class Resources for Non-Profits
Our experienced professionals proactively work with your organization to offer advice-driven solutions to help you achieve your objectives.








